preference.name: ARM_checkin_objects
preference.preference_description: Activates the system's check-in objects performance transaction. This measures the elapsed time from the beginning of the operation to when all objects are checked-in. Valid Values: * ON: Enables performance monitoring of the check in objects performance transaction. * OFF: Suppresses performance monitoring of the check in objects performance transaction.
